In [5]:
import os
dataset = r"C:\Users\Vasudevan P\Documents\Subhashree\CV Proj\train"
df = pd.DataFrame(columns = ["Name of image", "Species of image","actual image"])
df1 = pd.DataFrame(columns = ["Name of image", "Species of image","actual image"])
for i in os.listdir(dataset):
    if i!= '.DS_Store': 
     for j in os.listdir(os.path.join(dataset,i)):
        img = cv2.imread(os.path.join(dataset,i,j))     
        blurImg = cv2.GaussianBlur(img, (5,5),0)
        hsvImg = cv2.cvtColor(blurImg, cv2.COLOR_BGR2HSV)
        lower_green = (25, 40, 50)
        upper_green = (75, 255, 255)
        mask = cv2.inRange(hsvImg, lower_green, upper_green)
        kernel = cv2.getStructuringElement(cv2.MORPH_ELLIPSE,(11,11))
        mask = cv2.morphologyEx(mask,cv2.MORPH_CLOSE,kernel)
        bMask= mask >0
        clear = np.zeros_like(img, np.uint8) # Create empty image
        clear[bMask] = img[bMask] #Apply boolean mask to the origin image # Append image without background
        dict = {"Name of image" :j,
                "Species of image" :i,
                "actual image" :clear}
        dict1 = {"Name of image" :j,
                "Species of image" :i,
                "actual image" :img}
        df = df._append(dict,ignore_index = True) # With blurring"
        df1 = df1._append(dict1,ignore_index = True) # Without blurring"

In [10]:
def display(df,n):
    df = df.sample(n)
    for i,j in enumerate(df.iterrows()):
     pt.figure(figsize = (10,10))
     pt.subplot(1, n, i+1)
     pt.imshow(j[1]['actual image'])
     pt.title("{}".format(j[1]["Species of image"]))
     pt.show()

In [22]:
# # # 3. Model training
reset_seeds()
model = Sequential()
model.add(Conv2D(filters = 128,
                 kernel_size =3 ,
                 activation  = 'relu',
                 input_shape = (128,128,3)))
model.add(MaxPooling2D(pool_size = (2, 2)))
model.add(Conv2D(filters = 64,kernel_size = 3,activation = 'relu'))
model.add(MaxPooling2D(pool_size = (2, 2)))
model.add(Conv2D(filters = 64,kernel_size = 3,activation = 'relu'))
model.add(MaxPooling2D(pool_size = (2, 2)))
model.add(Conv2D(filters = 16,kernel_size = 3,activation = 'relu'))
model.add(MaxPooling2D(pool_size = (2, 2)))
model.add(Flatten())
model.add(Dense(128,activation = 'relu'))
model.add(Dropout(0.2))
model.add(Dense(64,activation = 'relu'))
model.add(Dense(32,activation = 'relu'))
model.add(Dense(12,activation = 'softmax'))
    
# Model Compiling
model.compile(optimizer = 'Adam',
              loss = 'categorical_crossentropy',
              metrics = 'accuracy')
